@startuml seq-04-password-reset
title Forgot + reset password (public)

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/auth" as API <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "SMTP / Email" as M <<external>>

== Forgot password ==
U -> B: Request reset (email)
B -> API: POST /auth/forgot-password { email }

API -> API: Zod validate + rate limit
API -> DB: findUnique user by email
opt User active
  API -> DB: deleteMany old PasswordResetToken
  API -> API: generate raw token, store hash + TTL
  API -> DB: passwordResetToken.create
  API -> M: sendPasswordResetEmail(resetUrl with raw token)
  API -> DB: logAuthEvent(PASSWORD_RESET_REQUESTED)
end
API -> API: min delay ~500ms + jitter\n(anti-enumeration)
API --> B: 200 generic message\n(always same wording)

== Reset password ==
U -> B: Submit new password + token from link
B -> API: POST /auth/reset-password { token, newPassword }

API -> API: Zod + rate limit
API -> API: hashResetToken(raw)
API -> DB: $transaction:\n find token + user\n update user passwordHash,\n authVersion++\n delete token row\n revoke all RefreshSessions
alt Invalid / expired token
  API --> B: 400 Invalid or expired reset link
else Success
  API -> DB: logAuthEvent(PASSWORD_RESET_COMPLETED)
  API --> B: 200 Password updated message
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/auth.ts** (~772+ forgot, ~819+ reset),
  **apps/api/src/lib/email.ts**.
end note

@enduml
